JSE-listed entertainment giant MultiChoice Group will be adding Disney+, a new direct-to-consumer streaming channel, to its DStv service from May 18, 2022. Confirming the move this week, MultiChoice said Disney+ will be available via the Explora Ultra decoder and will stream movies and shows from Disney, Pixar, Marvel, Star Wars and more. Read:
